---
import InvestLayout from '../../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout title="Financial Model" titleVi="Mô hình tài chính" noindex={true}>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="Mô hình tài chính">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 border border-red-400/30 rounded-full">Riêng tư</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Mô hình tài chính</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gold/10 border border-gold/30 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-sm text-gold">
        ⚠ Dự phóng tài chính là giả thuyết, không phải cam kết hay dự báo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4">Giả thuyết doanh thu</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-bg-border">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Gói</th>
              <th class="text-right py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Giá/tháng</th>
              <th class="text-right py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Thuê bao (Y1)</th>
              <th class="text-right py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Năm (giả thuyết)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-bg-border">
            {[
              { plan: 'Start', price: 'Free', subs: '500', rev: '$0' },
              { plan: 'Personal', price: '$12', subs: '200', rev: '$28.8K' },
              { plan: 'Family', price: '$24', subs: '150', rev: '$43.2K' },
              { plan: 'Creator', price: '$40', subs: '80', rev: '$38.4K' },
              { plan: 'Founder', price: '$80', subs: '50', rev: '$48K' },
              { plan: 'Business', price: '$200', subs: '20', rev: '$48K' },
              { plan: 'Chapter', price: '$320', subs: '10', rev: '$38.4K' },
              { plan: 'Enterprise', price: 'Custom', subs: '3', rev: '$150K' },
            ].map((row) => (
              <tr class="hover:bg-bg-soft/50">
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink">{row.plan}</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right text-ink-muted">{row.price}</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right text-ink-muted">{row.subs}</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right text-gold font-semibold">{row.rev}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
            <tr class="border-t-2 border-bg-border">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-ink" colspan="3">Tổng Y1 (giả thuyết)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-bold text-gold">~$394K</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-ink-dim italic">Tất cả số liệu là giả thuyết dựa trên chuẩn SaaS tương đương. Không phải dự báo.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4">Phân tích độ nhạy</h2>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-bg-border">
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Kịch bản</th>
              <th class="text-right py-2 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Thuê bao</th>
              <th class="text-right py-2 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Doanh thu Y1</th>
              <th class="text-right py-2 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Doanh thu Y3</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-bg-border">
            <tr><td class="py-2 text-ink">Thận trọng</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-ink-muted">50% giả thuyết</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$197K</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$1M</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 text-ink">Cơ sở</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-ink-muted">100% giả thuyết</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$394K</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$2.5M</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 text-ink">Lạc quan</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-ink-muted">200% giả thuyết</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$788K</td><td class="py-2 text-right text-gold">~$5M</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure locale="vi" /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
